Namespace: PanelButtonOpenableMixin

PanelButtonOpenableMixin

Mixin for openable panel buttons.

Example

var MoveTabButton = React.createClass({ mixins: [PanelButtonMixin, PanelButtonOpenableMixin],

handleClick: function(event) { var element = event.target, leftPanelId = Panel.getPanelByName(Left Panel).getId();

event.preventDefault();

} });
